title: War of the Roses: The Only Doggy You Like
description: Morgan went to her boyfriend's place a while back to find a girl sitting on his couch in his pajamas.  Morgan and the other girl confronted him and they both broke up with him.  Well Morgan went back to him and now thinks he's cheating again.  Once a cheater, always a cheater?
